IF OBJECT_ID(N'flow_materializations_v2', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE flow_materializations_v2 (
		materialization nvarchar(900) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		version nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		spec nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,

		PRIMARY KEY (materialization)
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'flow_checkpoints_v1', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE flow_checkpoints_v1 (
		materialization nvarchar(900) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		key_begin BIGINT NOT NULL,
		key_end BIGINT NOT NULL,
		fence BIGINT NOT NULL,
		"checkpoint" nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,

		PRIMARY KEY (materialization, key_begin, key_end)
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'Simple', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE "Simple" (
		id BIGINT NOT NULL,
		canary nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		flow_published_at DATETIME2 NOT NULL,
		flow_document nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,

		PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'duplicate_keys_standard', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE duplicate_keys_standard (
		id BIGINT NOT NULL,
		flow_published_at DATETIME2 NOT NULL,
		"int" BIGINT,
		str nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		flow_document nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,

		PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'duplicate_keys_delta', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE duplicate_keys_delta (
		id BIGINT NOT NULL,
		flow_published_at DATETIME2 NOT NULL,
		"int" BIGINT,
		str nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		flow_document nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'duplicate_keys_delta_exclude_flow_doc', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE duplicate_keys_delta_exclude_flow_doc (
		id BIGINT NOT NULL,
		flow_published_at DATETIME2 NOT NULL,
		"int" BIGINT,
		str nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'Multiple Types', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE "Multiple Types" (
		id BIGINT NOT NULL,
		array_int nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2,
		bool_field BIT,
		float_field DOUBLE PRECISION,
		flow_published_at DATETIME2 NOT NULL,
		multiple nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2,
		nested nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2,
		nullable_int BIGINT,
		str_field nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		flow_document nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,

		PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'Formatted Strings', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE "Formatted Strings" (
		id BIGINT NOT NULL,
		"date" DATE,
		datetime DATETIME2,
		flow_published_at DATETIME2 NOT NULL,
		int_and_str BIGINT,
		int_str BIGINT,
		num_and_str DOUBLE PRECISION,
		num_str DOUBLE PRECISION,
		"time" TIME,
		flow_document nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,

		PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
END;


IF OBJECT_ID(N'compound_key', 'U') IS NULL BEGIN
CREATE TABLE compound_key (
		yin nvarchar(900) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		yan nvarchar(900) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,
		flow_published_at DATETIME2 NOT NULL,
		num BIGINT NOT NULL,
		flow_document nvarchar(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2 NOT NULL,

		PRIMARY KEY (yin, yan)
);
END;
